      <![CDATA[<h2 id="背景"><a href="#背景" class="headerlink" title="背景"></a>背景</h2><p>我有两台OpenWRT,其中一台拥有公网IP,这一台作为主节点</p><h2 id="服务端"><a href="#服务端" class="headerlink" title="服务端"></a>服务端</h2><p>参考命令 不要直接使用</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">/usr/bin/easytier-core \</span><br><span class="line">  --network-name easytier \</span><br><span class="line">  --network-secret 这里填写密码 \</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 这里填写一个唯一IP</span></span><br><span class="line">  -i 10.14.14.1 \</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 这里填写内网网段(把服务端的网段分享给其他端)</span></span><br><span class="line">  -n 10.10.10.0/24 \</span><br><span class="line">  -r 15888 \</span><br><span class="line">  -l tcp:11010 \</span><br><span class="line">  -l udp:11010 \</span><br><span class="line">  -l ws:11011 \</span><br><span class="line">  -l wss:11012 \</span><br><span class="line">  --hostname iStoreOS \</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># tun网卡名称</span></span><br><span class="line">  --dev-name et_lan \</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 启用多线程</span></span><br><span class="line">  --multi-thread \</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 使用四个线程</span></span><br><span class="line">  --multi-thread-count 4 \</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 禁用ipv6,有v4公网完全不考虑v6哈哈</span></span><br><span class="line">  --disable-ipv6 \</span><br><span class="line">  --bind-device <span class="literal">false</span> \</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 设置加密方式</span></span><br><span class="line">  --encryption-algorithm xor \</span><br><span class="line">  --console-log-level info </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="客户端"><a href="#客户端" class="headerlink" title="客户端"></a>客户端</h2><p>参考命令 不要直接使用</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">/usr/bin/easytier-core \</span><br><span class="line">  --network-name easytier \</span><br><span class="line">  --network-secret 这里填写密码 \</span><br><span class="line">  -i 10.14.14.2 \</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 经过测试udp在我的网络上丢包很高，且tcp网速能够拉满上行，所有选择了tcp</span></span><br><span class="line">  -p tcp://这里填写你的服务端域名:11010 \</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 这里填写内网网段(把客户端的网段分享给其他端)</span></span><br><span class="line">  -n 172.18.0.0/24 \</span><br><span class="line">  -r 15888 \</span><br><span class="line">  --no-listener \</span><br><span class="line">  --hostname Netgear_R6800 \</span><br><span class="line">  -m easytier \</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># tun网卡名称</span></span><br><span class="line">  --dev-name et_lan \</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 启用多线程</span></span><br><span class="line">  --multi-thread \</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 使用四个线程</span></span><br><span class="line">  --multi-thread-count 4 \</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 禁用ipv6,有v4公网完全不考虑v6哈哈</span></span><br><span class="line">  --disable-ipv6 \</span><br><span class="line">  --bind-device <span class="literal">false</span> \</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 设置加密方式</span></span><br><span class="line">  --encryption-algorithm xor \</span><br><span class="line">  --console-log-level info </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/resource/openwrt-easytier/img.png" alt="img.png"></p>]]>
    </content>
